LeetCode 1 — Sort Array By Parity

sort_array_parity.py

class Solution:

    def sortArrayByParity(self, nums):

        even = list(filter(lambda x: x % 2 == 0, nums))
        odd = list(filter(lambda x: x % 2 != 0, nums))

        return even + odd


obj = Solution()

print(obj.sortArrayByParity([3,1,2,4]))

Output:

[2, 4, 3, 1]


